ask user if he wants to play a game of blackjack

if yes, print logo

give user and dealer two random cards,

print cards and score of user and ask if he want to hit or stand

if hit, draw another card as many times user wants to hit

if score over 21, reveal user and dealer hand and print BUST, you lose
else if user is satisfied, draw cards for dealer as long score of dealer is less than 17.

whenever an Ace is given to a participants, count value as 11 except score goes over 21, then count as 1.

reveal user and dealer cards and lock who is closer to 21